7482         this.node.parentNode.removeChild(this.node);
7483         this.shape && this.shape.parentNode.removeChild(this.shape);
7484         for (var i in this) {
7485             this[i] = typeof this[i] == "function" ? R._removedFactory(i) : null;
7486         }
7487         this.removed = true;
7488     };
7489     elproto.attr = function (name, value) {
7490         if (this.removed) {
7491             return this;
7492         }
7493         if (name == null) {
7494             var res = {};
7495             for (var a in this.attrs) if (this.attrs[has](a)) {
7496                 res[a] = this.attrs[a];
7497             }
7498             res.gradient && res.fill == "none" && (res.fill = res.gradient) && delete res.gradient;
7499             res.transform = this._.transform;
7500             return res;
7501         }
7502         if (value == null && R.is(name, "string")) {
7503             if (name == fillString && this.attrs.fill == "none" && this.attrs.gradient) {
7504                 return this.attrs.gradient;
7505             }
7506             var names = name.split(separator),
7507                 out = {};
7508             for (var i = 0, ii = names.length; i < ii; i++) {
7509                 name = names[i];
7510                 if (name in this.attrs) {
7511                     out[name] = this.attrs[name];
7512                 } else if (R.is(this.paper.customAttributes[name], "function")) {
7513                     out[name] = this.paper.customAttributes[name].def;
7514                 } else {
7515                     out[name] = R._availableAttrs[name];
7516                 }
7517             }
7518             return ii - 1 ? out : out[names[0]];
7519         }
7520         if (this.attrs && value == null && R.is(name, "array")) {
7521             out = {};
7522             for (i = 0, ii = name.length; i < ii; i++) {
7523                 out[name[i]] = this.attr(name[i]);
7524             }
7525             return out;
7526         }
7527         var params;
7528         if (value != null) {
7529             params = {};
7530             params[name] = value;
7531         }
7532         value == null && R.is(name, "object") && (params = name);
7533         for (var key in params) {
7534             eve("raphael.attr." + key + "." + this.id, this, params[key]);
7535         }
7536         if (params) {
7537             for (key in this.paper.customAttributes) if (this.paper.customAttributes[has](key) && params[has](key) && R.is(this.paper.customAttributes[key], "function")) {
7538                 var par = this.paper.customAttributes[key].apply(this, [].concat(params[key]));
7539                 this.attrs[key] = params[key];
7540                 for (var subkey in par) if (par[has](subkey)) {
7541                     params[subkey] = par[subkey];
7542                 }
7543             }
7544             // this.paper.canvas.style.display = "none";
7545             if (params.text && this.type == "text") {
7546                 this.textpath.string = params.text;
7547             }
7548             setFillAndStroke(this, params);
7549             // this.paper.canvas.style.display = E;
7550         }
7551         return this;
7552     };
7553     elproto.toFront = function () {
7554         !this.removed && this.node.parentNode.appendChild(this.node);
7555         this.paper && this.paper.top != this && R._tofront(this, this.paper);
7556         return this;
7557     };
7558     elproto.toBack = function () {
7559         if (this.removed) {
7560             return this;
7561         }
7562         if (this.node.parentNode.firstChild != this.node) {
7563             this.node.parentNode.insertBefore(this.node, this.node.parentNode.firstChild);
7564             R._toback(this, this.paper);
7565         }
7566         return this;
7567     };
7568     elproto.insertAfter = function (element) {
7569         if (this.removed) {
7570             return this;
7571         }
7572         if (element.constructor == R.st.constructor) {
7573             element = element[element.length - 1];
7574         }
7575         if (element.node.nextSibling) {
7576             element.node.parentNode.insertBefore(this.node, element.node.nextSibling);
7577         } else {
7578             element.node.parentNode.appendChild(this.node);
7579         }
7580         R._insertafter(this, element, this.paper);
7581         return this;
7582     };
7583     elproto.insertBefore = function (element) {
7584         if (this.removed) {
7585             return this;
7586         }
7587         if (element.constructor == R.st.constructor) {
7588             element = element[0];
7589         }
7590         element.node.parentNode.insertBefore(this.node, element.node);
7591         R._insertbefore(this, element, this.paper);
7592         return this;
7593     };
7594     elproto.blur = function (size) {
7595         var s = this.node.runtimeStyle,
7596             f = s.filter;
7597         f = f.replace(blurregexp, E);
7598         if (+size !== 0) {
7599             this.attrs.blur = size;
7600             s.filter = f + S + ms + ".Blur(pixelradius=" + (+size || 1.5) + ")";
7601             s.margin = R.format("-{0}px 0 0 -{0}px", round(+size || 1.5));
7602         } else {
7603             s.filter = f;
7604             s.margin = 0;
7605             delete this.attrs.blur;
7606         }
7607         return this;
7608     };
7609 
7610     R._engine.path = function (pathString, vml) {
7611         var el = createNode("shape");
7612         el.style.cssText = cssDot;
7613         el.coordsize = zoom + S + zoom;
7614         el.coordorigin = vml.coordorigin;
7615         var p = new Element(el, vml),
7616             attr = {fill: "none", stroke: "#000"};
7617         pathString && (attr.path = pathString);
7618         p.type = "path";
7619         p.path = [];
7620         p.Path = E;
7621         setFillAndStroke(p, attr);
7622         vml.canvas.appendChild(el);
7623         var skew = createNode("skew");
7624         skew.on = true;
7625         el.appendChild(skew);
7626         p.skew = skew;
7627         p.transform(E);
7628         return p;
7629     };
7630     R._engine.rect = function (vml, x, y, w, h, r) {
7631         var path = R._rectPath(x, y, w, h, r),
7632             res = vml.path(path),
7633             a = res.attrs;
7634         res.X = a.x = x;
7635         res.Y = a.y = y;
7636         res.W = a.width = w;
7637         res.H = a.height = h;
7638         a.r = r;
7639         a.path = path;
7640         res.type = "rect";
7641         return res;
7642     };
7643     R._engine.ellipse = function (vml, x, y, rx, ry) {
7644         var res = vml.path(),
7645             a = res.attrs;
7646         res.X = x - rx;
7647         res.Y = y - ry;
7648         res.W = rx * 2;
7649         res.H = ry * 2;
7650         res.type = "ellipse";
7651         setFillAndStroke(res, {
7652             cx: x,
7653             cy: y,
7654             rx: rx,
7655             ry: ry
7656         });
7657         return res;
7658     };
7659     R._engine.circle = function (vml, x, y, r) {
7660         var res = vml.path(),
7661             a = res.attrs;
7662         res.X = x - r;
7663         res.Y = y - r;
7664         res.W = res.H = r * 2;
7665         res.type = "circle";
7666         setFillAndStroke(res, {
7667             cx: x,
7668             cy: y,
7669             r: r
7670         });
7671         return res;
7672     };
7673     R._engine.image = function (vml, src, x, y, w, h) {
7674         var path = R._rectPath(x, y, w, h),
7675             res = vml.path(path).attr({stroke: "none"}),
7676             a = res.attrs,
7677             node = res.node,
7678             fill = node.getElementsByTagName(fillString)[0];
7679         a.src = src;
7680         res.X = a.x = x;
7681         res.Y = a.y = y;
7682         res.W = a.width = w;
7683         res.H = a.height = h;
7684         a.path = path;
7685         res.type = "image";
7686         fill.parentNode == node && node.removeChild(fill);
7687         fill.rotate = true;
7688         fill.src = src;
7689         fill.type = "tile";
7690         res._.fillpos = [x, y];
7691         res._.fillsize = [w, h];
7692         node.appendChild(fill);
7693         setCoords(res, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0);
7694         return res;
7695     };
7696     R._engine.text = function (vml, x, y, text) {
7697         var el = createNode("shape"),
7698             path = createNode("path"),
7699             o = createNode("textpath");
7700         x = x || 0;
7701         y = y || 0;
7702         text = text || "";
7703         path.v = R.format("m{0},{1}l{2},{1}", round(x * zoom), round(y * zoom), round(x * zoom) + 1);
7704         path.textpathok = true;
7705         o.string = Str(text);
7706         o.on = true;
7707         el.style.cssText = cssDot;
7708         el.coordsize = zoom + S + zoom;
7709         el.coordorigin = "0 0";
7710         var p = new Element(el, vml),
7711             attr = {
7712                 fill: "#000",
7713                 stroke: "none",
7714                 font: R._availableAttrs.font,
7715                 text: text
7716             };
7717         p.shape = el;
7718         p.path = path;
7719         p.textpath = o;
7720         p.type = "text";
7721         p.attrs.text = Str(text);
7722         p.attrs.x = x;
7723         p.attrs.y = y;
7724         p.attrs.w = 1;
7725         p.attrs.h = 1;
7726         setFillAndStroke(p, attr);
7727         el.appendChild(o);
7728         el.appendChild(path);
7729         vml.canvas.appendChild(el);
7730         var skew = createNode("skew");
7731         skew.on = true;
7732         el.appendChild(skew);
7733         p.skew = skew;
7734         p.transform(E);
7735         return p;
7736     };
7737     R._engine.setSize = function (width, height) {
7738         var cs = this.canvas.style;
7739         this.width = width;
7740         this.height = height;
7741         width == +width && (width += "px");
7742         height == +height && (height += "px");
7743         cs.width = width;
7744         cs.height = height;
7745         cs.clip = "rect(0 " + width + " " + height + " 0)";
7746         if (this._viewBox) {
7747             R._engine.setViewBox.apply(this, this._viewBox);
7748         }
7749         return this;
7750     };
7751     R._engine.setViewBox = function (x, y, w, h, fit) {
7752         R.eve("raphael.setViewBox", this, this._viewBox, [x, y, w, h, fit]);
7753         var paperSize = this.getSize(),
7754             width = paperSize.width,
7755             height = paperSize.height,
7756             H, W;
7757         if (fit) {
7758             H = height / h;
7759             W = width / w;
7760             if (w * H < width) {
7761                 x -= (width - w * H) / 2 / H;
7762             }
7763             if (h * W < height) {
7764                 y -= (height - h * W) / 2 / W;
7765             }
7766         }
7767         this._viewBox = [x, y, w, h, !!fit];
7768         this._viewBoxShift = {
7769             dx: -x,
7770             dy: -y,
7771             scale: paperSize
7772         };
7773         this.forEach(function (el) {
7774             el.transform("...");
7775         });
7776         return this;
7777     };
7778     var createNode;
7779     R._engine.initWin = function (win) {
7780             var doc = win.document;
7781             if (doc.styleSheets.length < 31) {
7782                 doc.createStyleSheet().addRule(".rvml", "behavior:url(#default#VML)");
7783             } else {
7784                 // no more room, add to the existing one
7785                 // http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms531194%28VS.85%29.aspx
7786                 doc.styleSheets[0].addRule(".rvml", "behavior:url(#default#VML)");
7787             }
7788             try {
7789                 !doc.namespaces.rvml && doc.namespaces.add("rvml", "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml");
7790                 createNode = function (tagName) {
7791                     return doc.createElement('<rvml:' + tagName + ' class="rvml">');
7792                 };
7793             } catch (e) {
7794                 createNode = function (tagName) {
7795                     return doc.createElement('<' + tagName + ' xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft.com:vml" class="rvml">');
7796                 };
7797             }
7798         };
7799     R._engine.initWin(R._g.win);
7800     R._engine.create = function () {
7801         var con = R._getContainer.apply(0, arguments),
7802             container = con.container,
7803             height = con.height,
7804             s,
7805             width = con.width,
7806             x = con.x,
7807             y = con.y;
7808         if (!container) {
7809             throw new Error("VML container not found.");
7810         }
7811         var res = new R._Paper,
7812             c = res.canvas = R._g.doc.createElement("div"),
7813             cs = c.style;
7814         x = x || 0;
7815         y = y || 0;
7816         width = width || 512;
7817         height = height || 342;
7818         res.width = width;
7819         res.height = height;
7820         width == +width && (width += "px");
7821         height == +height && (height += "px");
7822         res.coordsize = zoom * 1e3 + S + zoom * 1e3;
7823         res.coordorigin = "0 0";
7824         res.span = R._g.doc.createElement("span");
7825         res.span.style.cssText = "position:absolute;left:-9999em;top:-9999em;padding:0;margin:0;line-height:1;";
7826         c.appendChild(res.span);
7827         cs.cssText = R.format("top:0;left:0;width:{0};height:{1};display:inline-block;position:relative;clip:rect(0 {0} {1} 0);overflow:hidden", width, height);
7828         if (container == 1) {
7829             R._g.doc.body.appendChild(c);
7830             cs.left = x + "px";
7831             cs.top = y + "px";
7832             cs.position = "absolute";
7833         } else {
7834             if (container.firstChild) {
7835                 container.insertBefore(c, container.firstChild);
7836             } else {
7837                 container.appendChild(c);
7838             }
7839         }
7840         res.renderfix = function () {};
7841         return res;
7842     };
7843     R.prototype.clear = function () {
7844         R.eve("raphael.clear", this);
7845         this.canvas.innerHTML = E;
7846         this.span = R._g.doc.createElement("span");
7847         this.span.style.cssText = "position:absolute;left:-9999em;top:-9999em;padding:0;margin:0;line-height:1;display:inline;";
7848         this.canvas.appendChild(this.span);
7849         this.bottom = this.top = null;
7850     };
7851     R.prototype.remove = function () {
7852         R.eve("raphael.remove", this);
7853         this.canvas.parentNode.removeChild(this.canvas);
7854         for (var i in this) {
7855             this[i] = typeof this[i] == "function" ? R._removedFactory(i) : null;
7856         }
7857         return true;
7858     };

7860     var setproto = R.st;
7861     for (var method in elproto) if (elproto[has](method) && !setproto[has](method)) {
7862         setproto[method] = (function (methodname) {
7863             return function () {
7864                 var arg = arguments;
7865                 return this.forEach(function (el) {
7866                     el[methodname].apply(el, arg);
7867                 });
7868             };
7869         })(method);
7870     }
